<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css"> --}}
    <link 
    rel="stylesheet" 
    type="text/css"
    media="print"
    onload="this.media='all'" 
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Roboto+Condensed:wght@400;700&display=swap">
    <style>
        body, html {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #F7F7F7;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 670px) {
            body, html {
                background-color: white;
            }
        }

        a {
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            -webkit-transition: all ease .3s;
            transition: all ease .3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: orange;
        }

        .root {
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .root section {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            display: -webkit-box;
            display: -ms-flexbox;
            display: flex;
            -webkit-box-pack: center;
                -ms-flex-pack: center;
                    justify-content: center;
            -webkit-box-align: center;
                -ms-flex-align: center;
                    align-items: center;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            -webkit-box-direction: normal;
                -ms-flex-direction: column;
                    flex-direction: column;
        }

        .root section .logo-wrapper {
            display: -webkit-box;
            display: -ms-flexbox;
            display: flex;
            -webkit-box-align: center;
                -ms-flex-align: center;
                    align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 670px) {
            .root section .logo-wrapper {
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }
        }

        .root section .logo-wrapper .logo-text {
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
            font-family: 'raleway', sans-serif;
            margin-left: 16px;
        }

        .root section .logo-wrapper .logo-text h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 4px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .root section .logo-wrapper .logo-text p {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .root section .logo-wrapper .logo {
            height: 40px;
            width: 40px;
        }

        .root section .card-content {
            margin-top: 21px;
            background-color: white;
            -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
                    box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 670px) {
            .root section .card-content {
                background-color: transparent;
                -webkit-box-shadow: none;
                        box-shadow: none;
                padding: 12px 0px;
                width: 100%;
                word-wrap: break-word;
                margin-top: 0;
            }
        }

        .root section .card-content .content {
            font-family: 'roboto-condensed', sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 27px;
            padding: 21px 32px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 670px) {
            .root section .card-content .content {
                padding: 24px;
                word-wrap: break-word;
            }
        }

        .root section .card-content .content .sign {
            margin-top: 30px;
            line-height: 8px;
        }

        .root section .card-content .content .table {
            margin: 16px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .root section .card-content .content .table {
                font-size: 8px;
            }
        }

        .root section .card-content .content .table tr {
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 21px;
        }

        .root section .card-content .content .table tr td:nth-child(2) {
            width: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .root .decoration--right {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 0;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 30%;
            }

        .root .decoration--left {
        position: absolute;
        z-index: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 30%;
        }
        
            /*# sourceMappingURL=style.css.map */
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
      <p>img sudah di attach vector sudah png dan css sudah internal</p>
      <p>vector sudah tampil tapi belum jadi background</p>
        <div class="root">
            <section>
                <div class="logo-wrapper">
                    <img src="cid:icon.webp" alt="icon" class="logo">
                    <div class="logo-text">
                        <h3>RPL-GDC</h3>
                        <p>Brainspark</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Halo {{name}}</h3>
                        <p>Terima kasih telah medaftar brainspark dengan tema <b>{{eventTheme}}</b> oleh <b>{{speaker}}</b></p>
                        <p>kamu bisa menghadiri acara ini pada:</p>
                        
                        <div class="table">
                            <table>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Tanggal</th>
                                    <td>:</td>
                                    <td>{{date}}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Jam</th>
                                    <td>:</td>
                                    <td>{{time}}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Lokasi</th>
                                    <td>:</td>
                                    <td>
                                        {{!-- <script>
                                            handlebars.registerHelper('ifCond', function(v1, v2, options) {
                                                if(v1 < v2) {
                                                    return options.fn(this);
                                                }
                                                return options.inverse(this);
                                            });
                                        </script> --}}
                                        {{!-- {{#pf:ifCond location 2 }}
                                            <a href={{location}}</a>
                                        {{else}}
                                            <p>location > 2</p> 
                                        {{/pf:ifCond}} --}}
                                        {{#pf:if linklength ">" "1"}}
                                            <a href={{link}}>{{location}}</a>
                                        {{else}}
                                            <p>{{location}}</p>
                                        {{/pf:if}} 
                                        
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>

                        <p>Kami harap kamu dapat menghadiri acara ini dan mendapat pengalaman berharga.</p>

                        <div class="sign">
                            <h4>Terimakasih</h4>
                            <p>RPL-GDC Laboratory</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <div class="decoration">
                <img src="cid:Vector5.png" class="decoration--left" alt="vector left bottom">
                <img src="cid:Vector6.png" class="decoration--right" alt="vector right top">
            </div> 
        </div>
  </body>
</html>